text: Prosopocera alboplagiata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Karl Jordan in 1894. It is known from Sierra Leone and Ghana.BioLib.cz - Prosopocera alboplagiata. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1894
